<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c2">(بَاب الْخَاء)</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>٢٤٤٣ -<span class="c5"> أَبُو خَالِد:</span> حَكِيم بن حزَام بن<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>خويلد بن أَسد الْقرشِي , لَهُ صُحْبَة.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>عَاشَ مائَة وَعشْرين سنة - سِتِّينَ فِي الْجَاهِلِيَّة ,<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>وَسِتِّينَ فِي الْإِسْلَام -.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>أخبرنَا أَحْمد بن الْحسن بن عتبَة , ثَنَا عبد الله<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>ابْن عِيسَى الْمَدِينِيّ ,<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span> سَمِعت إِبْرَاهِيم بن<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>الْمُنْذر الْحزَامِي ,<span class="c5"> يَقُول:</span> حَكِيم بن حزَام يكنى:<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>أَبَا خَالِد.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>٢٤٤٤ -<span class="c5"> أَبُو خَالِد:</span> يزِيد بن أبي سُفْيَان<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>صَخْر بن حَرْب.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>أحد أُمَرَاء الأجناد.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>مَاتَ فِي خلَافَة عمر بِالشَّام فِي طاعون عمواس<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>قَالَه الْهَيْثَم بن عدي وكناه.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>٢٤٤٥ -<span class="c5"> أَبُو خَالِد:</span> وَقيل: أَبُو خلف: يعلى<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span>ابْن أُميَّة.<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span>كناه الْهَيْثَم بن عدي.<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span>٢٤٤٦ -<span class="c5"> أَبُو خَالِد:</span> السّلمِيّ.<a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p19"></span>لَهُ صُحْبَة.<a href="#p19" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p20"></span><span class="c5">روى حَدِيثه:</span> مُحَمَّد بن خَالِد , عَن أَبِيه , عَن<a href="#p20" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p21"></span>جده.<a href="#p21" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p22"></span>٢٤٤٧ -<span class="c5"> أَبُو خَالِد:</span> لَهُ صُحْبَة , غير مُسَمّى.<a href="#p22" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p23"></span><span class="c5">روى:</span> وَكِيع , عَن مَالك بن الْحَارِث , عَن أبي<a href="#p23" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p24"></span>خَالِد , وَكَانَ لَهُ صُحْبَة , أَنه وَفد على عمر<a href="#p24" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p25"></span>رَضِي الله عَنهُ.<a href="#p25" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p26"></span><span class="c2">(وَمن التَّابِعين)</span><a href="#p26" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p27"></span>٢٤٤٨ - أَبُو خَالِد.<a href="#p27" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p28"></span><span class="c5">حدث عَن:</span> ابْن مَسْعُود.<a href="#p28" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p29"></span><span class="c5">روى حَدِيثه:</span> عبد الله بن رَجَاء , عَن مُحَمَّد<a href="#p29" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p30"></span>ابْن مُسلم , عَن أبي ثُمَامَة عَنهُ.<a href="#p30" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p31"></span>٢٤٤٩ -<span class="c5"> أَبُو خَالِد:</span> مولى لآل جعدة بن<a href="#p31" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p32"></span>هُبَيْرَة.<a href="#p32" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p33"></span><span class="c5">حدث عَن:</span> أبي هُرَيْرَة.<a href="#p33" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p34"></span><span class="c5">روى عَنهُ:</span> أَبُو خَالِد الدالاني.<a href="#p34" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p35"></span>وروى <span class="c2">(ق ١٠٣ / ب)</span> مَنْصُور , عَن أبي<a href="#p35" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p36"></span>خَالِد , عَن مَيْمُونَة.<a href="#p36" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p37"></span>أرَاهُ هَذَا.<a href="#p37" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p38"></span>٢٤٥٠ -<span class="c5"> أَبُو خَالِد:</span> مولى الْأَنْصَار.<a href="#p38" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p39"></span>عداده فِي أهل مصر.<a href="#p39" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p40"></span><span class="c5">روى عَنهُ:</span> بكر بن سوَادَة.<a href="#p40" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p41"></span>قَالَه أَبُو سعيد بن يُونُس.<a href="#p41" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p42"></span>٢٤٥١ -<span class="c5"> أَبُو خَالِد:</span> الْكُوفِي.<a href="#p42" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p43"></span><span class="c5">حدث عَن:</span> ابْن عَبَّاس.<a href="#p43" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p44"></span><span class="c5">روى عَنهُ:</span> إِسْمَاعِيل بن حَمَّاد بن أبي حنيفَة<a href="#p44" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p45"></span>فِي الْجَهْر بِبسْم الله الرَّحْمَن الرَّحِيم.<a href="#p45" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p46"></span>٢٤٥٢ -<span class="c5"> أَبُو خَالِد:</span> الْكِنَانِي.<a href="#p46" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p47"></span><span class="c5">حدث عَن:</span> ابْن مَسْعُود.<a href="#p47" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p48"></span><span class="c5">روى عَنهُ:</span> أَبُو إِسْحَاق السبيعِي.<a href="#p48" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p49"></span>٢٤٥٣ -<span class="c5"> أَبُو خَالِد:</span> المَخْزُومِي.<a href="#p49" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>